====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to be [[durable]]; to be able to [[withstand]]
#: {{zh-x|耐火|fire '''resistant'''}}
# to [[bear]]; to [[endure]]
#: {{zh-x|吃苦耐勞|{{q|literally}} to consume bitterness and to '''endure''' hardship}}
# {{lb|zh|Cantonese|Southern Pinghua|of time}} [[long#Adjective|long]]; taking a long time to [[happen]]
#: {{zh-x|我 已經 等 咗 好 耐 喇！|I've already waited '''forever'''!|C}}
#: {{zh-x|架 巴士{si6-2} 咁 耐 都 未 嚟 㗎？|Why is the bus taking so '''long''' to arrive?|C}}
# {{lb|zh|literary}} to be [[worth]]; to [[merit]]; to [[deserve]]; to be [[worthy]] of
# {{lb|zh|literary}} [[suitable]]; [[appropriate]]
# {{lb|zh|literary}} an [[ancient]] [[punishment]] involving [[shaving]] one's [[beard]] and [[temple]]s

